    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      189.23,
      520.48,
      269.24
    ],
    "text": "On 20.07.2026, a team of officers attached to the Kadanegedara Police, acting on a tip-off, conducted a raid in the Kankaniyamulla area within the Kadanegedara Police Division and arrested a suspect in possession of 15 l (20 bottles) of illicit liquor and 1,025 l (06 barrels) of fermented wash (\"Goda\") used in the illicit production of liquor.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      283.82,
      386.14,
      299.36
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 30-year-old resident of Yakwila.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
