    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      189.23,
      525.85,
      285.32
    ],
    "text": "On the evening of 20.07.2026, officers attached to the Negombo Divisional Criminal Investigation Bureau, acting on information received, conducted a raid in the Dalupotha area within the Negombo Police Division and arrested a suspect found in possession of 56 l and 250 ml (75 bottles) of illicit liquor. The suspect was subsequently handed over to the Negombo Police Station for further legal action.",
