    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 20.07.2026, a fatal road traffic accident occurred in the Thonigala area along the Ana maduwa \u2013 Puttalam Road within the Anamaduwa Police Division when a bus travelling from Puttalam to Anamaduwa collided with a motorcycle travelling in the opposite direction.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
